-- Assad Promises to Have Syria Under Control Soon, Chavez says
-- B y   C o r i n a   P o n s
-- 2012-04-07T00:59:07Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-07/assad-promises-to-have-syria-under-control-soon-chavez-says.html
Venezuelan President  Hugo Chavez ,
speaking by phone on state television, said Syrian President
Bashar al-Assad promised to have his country under control soon
with minimal victims. Chavez said he spoke with Assad by phone
earlier today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Corina Pons in Caracas at 
 crpons@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Paul Tighe at 
 ptighe@bloomberg.net  